      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MRIYA DREAM (8) scored at this track two runs ago before having his colours lowered when second at his latest appearance over 1684m at this track, beaten 3.5 metres. Can settle just behind them and wait on the sprint lane. Won't find this any harder and he can give this a mighty shake. LOTS OF CHANGE (4) found a couple better two runs back then things went sour last time when he suffered interference and broke, finishing 17 metres back in fifth over 2116m at this track. Meets a similar line up so he is sure to be a force with even luck. MAJESTIC LINE (5) is close to a win after two successive seconds, the latest over 2116m at this track. Capable of taking this out. ELISH STAR (2) showed pleasing improvement last time out when runner-up over 1684m at this track.",
